casebody.data:
Myeong H. CHOI, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
James Jin CHOI, Defendant-Respondent. C-299 September Term 2017
079561 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 14, 2017

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000757-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
